UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2428
1 AN ACT relating to public safety.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 95.200 is amended to read as follows:
4 (1) Each member of the police force, including special police officers[policemen],
5 before entering upon the discharge of his or her duties, shall take an oath to
6 faithfully discharge the duties of his or her office.
7 (2) This oath shall be subscribed by the person taking it and filed in the office of the
8 department of public safety.
